                <h1 class="text-center">Measuring What Matters: The Analytics Framework</h1>
                <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-center">A data-driven marketing strategy requires a robust framework for measuring performance, demonstrating ROI, and optimizing spend. This framework focuses on the full funnel, from initial awareness to customer expansion, incorporating both sales-led and product-led KPIs.</p>
