                        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <li><strong>Marketing Qualified Leads (MQLs)</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>Cost per MQL</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>Website Traffic & Conversion Rate</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>SEO Keyword Rankings</strong></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 visual-content">
                        <h3>Product-Led Growth (PLG)</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <li><strong>Free Trial / Demo Signups</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>Product Qualified Leads (PQLs)</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>Activation Rate</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>Time to Value (TTV)</strong></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 visual-content">
                        <h3>Bottom of Funnel</h3>
                        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm">
                            <li><strong>Sales Qualified Leads (SQLs)</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>MQL-to-SQL Conversion Rate</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>Marketing-Sourced Pipeline ($)</strong></li>
                            <li><strong>Customer Acquisition Cost (CAC)</strong></li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                     <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-200 visual-content">
                        <h3>Customer & Revenue</h3>
